( I wasn't sure if healing fully from the CR chamber was moding.  I'm 
sorry if it was.  Let me know and I shall correct it)

::Shadow Wing::

She looked up and saw Prowl.
"Yeah cover us for a moment.  He need to go to the CR and get his 
optics fixed."  She looked back at Lunarpine.
"I know that you can slagg me faster than any pred here.  But don't 
argue with me on this.  Come with me inside the ark and get into a 
chamber.  You'll fight better if you can see your opponant."

She placed her good hand over Lunarpines.
"Now be quite and follow me."  She led him into the ark.
